          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1586957754215-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> smoked basa pieces</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Pour the <strong>béchamel sauce</strong> over the <strong>smoked basa</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> drained potatoes</strong> (reserve the pot) and put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until golden and bubbling</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1586957764540-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1586957764540-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1586957764540-x700.jpg",
