          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the bake is golden and bubbling, reboil a kettle</p><p>Remove the dish from the oven and leave to stand for 5-6 mins – this is your <strong>smoky fish & potato bake</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>trimmed</strong> <strong>green beans</strong> and <strong>blanched peas</strong> to the reserved pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cover with <strong>boiled water</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5 min or until tender – this is your<strong> green veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
